### **4. 27_StreamLineGraph**  
**Description:**  
Displays incoming numerical data as a real-time scrolling line chart.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# StreamLineGraph - Live Data Visualizer

StreamLineGraph is ideal for showing real-time metric streams in dashboards, demos, or analytics tools.

## Features
- Live updating chart  
- Adjustable speed  
- Clean design  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/27_StreamLineGraph.git
cd 27_StreamLineGraph
python visualize.py
